messages.message: Hi did we release to prod today? Have a few fixes i’m waiting on for work tomorrow.
do you mean instabae.com (http://instabae.com)? our weekly deployment is scheduled on Tuesdays

Yep IB.com (http://IB.com). I’m currently blocked on a POV due to this bug (https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/SBB-133). Is there anyway I can get access to this fix before Tuesday? I really need it tomorrow ready for a meeting first thing next week.

cc: @Kerry

hmm actually we were planning to do a deployment tonight after we certify 23.04.4 which should include this fix, because we plan to GA that version next Monday.
but just for the record we don't do adhoc deployments to instabase.com (http://instabase.com) for individual fix, otherwise there will be too much down time to the site. sandboxes can be utilized for that.
